<Algorithm code="             1. Let _bindingObject_ be _envRec_.[[BindingObject]].             1. Let _foundBinding_ be ? HasProperty(_bindingObject_, _N_).             1. If _foundBinding_ is *false*, return *false*.             1. If _envRec_.[[IsWithEnvironment]] is *false*, return *true*.             1. Let _unscopables_ be ? Get(_bindingObject_, %Symbol.unscopables%).             1. If _unscopables_ is an Object, then               1. Let _blocked_ be ToBoolean(? Get(_unscopables_, _N_)).               1. If _blocked_ is *true*, return *false*.             1. Return *true*.           ">
